text: Sancta maria wæsXVIgear eald þa heo crist akende, & syþþan heo wæs mid himXXXIIIgeara on middanearde.
And heo leofodeXIIIgear æfter him her on worulde, & heo wæsLXIIIgeara eald þa heo forðferde.
And se hælend wæsXXXgeara eald þa hine man fullode, &XXXIIIgeara eald þa he þrowode for us.
Adam wæs her on worulde lifesIXhund geara, &XXXgeara.
Adam wæs on helle æfter his forðsiðe, & ealle þa gewitenan sawla mid him oð þone dæg þe ure drihten crist þrowode.
Noe hæfdeIIIsuna þus wæron hatene, Sem, cham, Iafeð.
Of þam þreom awocan & forð comanLXXIIþeoda, fram IafeðeXV, & fram chameXXX, & fram SemeXXVII.
